          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Kreisdiagramm zeigt die Prozentsätze der

          </description>

            <string language="x-mt-fr">Ce diagramme circulaire circulaire montre les

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta carta de torta mostra as porcentagens da

            <string language="x-mt-it">Questo diagramma a torta mostra le percentuali di
